20 WHEREAS, Lawrence Ervin Bearden, formerly of Smackover, Arkansas,
21 passed away on Monday, February 3, 2025, at the age of eighty-six (86); and
22
23 WHEREAS, Lawrence Ervin Bearden was born in Chidester, Arkansas, on
24 April 14, 1938, to Walter and Ruby Bearden, and he graduated from Fairview
25 High School before earning a bachelor's degree in Business Administration
26 from Southern State College (now Southern Arkansas University) in Magnolia in
27 1961; and
28
29 WHEREAS, during his time at Southern State College, Lawrence Ervin
30 Bearden served as President of the Student Government Association and was an
31 active member of the Wesley Foundation, where he met Ann Oliver, the love of
32 his life; and
33
34 WHEREAS, Lawrence Ervin Bearden and Ann Oliver married in 1961 and
35 shared sixty-three (63) years of devoted marriage; and
